                    <td>
                        <p>(1)</p>
                    </td>
                    <td></td>
                    <td colspan="4">
                        
                        <p class="align_justified">For the purposes of item 2, the gross floor area
                            of a building
                            is
                            the area contained within the external walls of the building measured at
                            each floor level (including any floor below the level of the ground),
                            together with the area of each balcony in the building, which
                            is
                            calculated
                            from
