                        <p>(2)</p>
                    </td>
                    <td></td>
                    <td colspan="4">
                        
                        <p class="align_justified">For the purposes of item 3, the gross floor area
                            is
                            the roofed-over area used exclusively for the business of the
                            restaurant,
                            food
                            factory (whether or not for preparation of bakery products only),
                            factory canteen or composite food
                            shop.
                            It includes store-rooms, cold storage chambers, staff changing rooms,
                            offices, air-conditioning engine rooms, working areas, kitchens,
                            lavatories, lift lobbies, stair halls and any space used exclusively by
                            the restaurant,
                            food
                            factory (whether or not for preparation of bakery products only),
                            factory canteen or composite food
                            shop.</p>
