        2025</ref>)</sourceNote><section id="ID_1758790622902_001" name="s4" temporalId="s4" startPeriod="2025-11-01" status="operational" reason="inEffect"><num value="4">4.</num><heading>Transitional
            provisions relating to Fire Services Department (Reports and Certificates) (Amendment)
            Regulation 2025</heading><subsection id="ID_1761634113085_001" name="1" temporalId="s4_1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content>The amended Regulations do not apply in relation to a specified application
                made before the commencement date in relation to any of the premises specified in
                item 3 of the Table in <ref>regulation 3</ref> of the pre-amended Regulations
                        (<b><i>subject application</i></b>).</content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1761634113085_002" name="2" temporalId="s4_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content>The pre-amended Regulations continue to apply in relation to the subject
                application as if the 2025 Amendment Regulation had not been made.</content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1761634113085_003" name="3" temporalId="s4_3"><num value="3">(3)</num><leadIn>In this regulation—</leadIn><def name="2025AmendmentRegulation"><term>2025 Amendment Regulation</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">《2025年修訂規例》</term>) means the Fire Services Department (Reports and
                Certificates) (Amendment) Regulation 2025;</def><def name="AmendedRegulations"><term>amended Regulations</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">《經修訂規例》</term>) means
                these regulations as amended by the 2025 Amendment Regulation;</def><def name="CommencementDate">*<term>commencement date</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">生效日期</term>) means the
                date on which the 2025 Amendment Regulation comes into operation;</def><def name="PreamendedRegulations"><term>pre-amended Regulations</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">《原有規例》</term>)
